    "(2) and (3).",
    "When the optimization process should end is decided by the termination criterion.",
    "The maximum number of iterations is used in this paper to define the termination criterion.",
    "Once this requirement is met, the MBWO algorithm reports the best beluga whale position, which is the optimal combination of dropout period, learning rate, and batch size that produced the best performance during the optimization process.",
